  ["...Heh. (a long beat) Nah — you know what? Keep her, hermano. She kept YOU breathin' while I couldn't. Just don't let her sit, V. She hates that."] = "...Je. (una larga pausa) Nel — ¿sabes qué? Quédatela, hermano. Ella te mantuvo VIVA mientras yo no pude. Solo no la dejes parada, V. Eso lo odia.",
